      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one and is in truly flawless condition\u2014inside and out! It still has that fresh, new-car feel and drives like it just rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that's been loved and looks absolutely stunning, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
