    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, meticulously maintained to preserve its analog purity. The S54 straight-six features a fully overhauled high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power to the rear wheels via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual and a factory limited-slip differential. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and documented rod bearing replacement, addressing critical longitudinal stress points common to the chassis. Suspension geometry remains factory-spec with zero bushing play, providing surgical turn-in and maintaining the legendary 50/50 weight distribution. The exterior finish is flawless with consistent paint depth across all panels, while the cabin remains a time capsule with pristine Nappa leather and no delamination of the interior trim. A turn-key collector piece with zero mechanical compromise.",
      "price": 48500.0,
