      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a vehicle in absolute showroom condition that satisfies even the most discerning collector. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, while the interior remains in a time-capsule state, retaining that distinct new-car aroma and supple, untouched leather seating. Every service has been meticulously documented and performed exclusively at certified dealerships, ensuring the mechanical integrity is as flawless as the aesthetic. Garage-kept since day one and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the pinnacle of its model year. From the pristine engine bay to the unmarked alloy wheels, no detail has been overlooked. This is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
